{{lua|Module:Sports color}}
This template is designed to be used with templates to automatically apply the color to a link corresponding to the primary style for a team in [[Major League Baseball]] and other professional leagues. It can be used in conjunction with [[Template:Baseball primary color]].

== Usage ==
<pre>{{Baseball primary link|TEAMNAME|link target|link text}}</pre>
or
<pre>{{Baseball primary link|TEAMNAME|link target}}</pre>

For example:

<pre>
{{Baseball primary link|Arizona Diamondbacks|Arizona}}
{{Baseball primary link|Miami Marlins|Miami}}
</pre>

=== Supported teams ===
See [[Module:Sports color/baseball]].

